Open firebase, create a new proyect, go to config, go all the way to firebase SDK snippet
and then change to config and copy the info. Create a new file named firebase.js and paste the info 

Then go to authentication, Sign-in method, select the one you want and enable it and click done.

open up a second terminal and write:

    npm install -g firebase-tools
    npm install firebase


if founded vulnerabilities, check if you are in the correct folder in this case "amazon-clone".